Pomodo7o is a pomodoro timer that highlights Windows 7 features.  Namely the taskbar progress indicator and thumbnail toolbars.

---------------
v0.3
Gracefully degrade for non Windows 7 systems.
Add "toolbar" for those with non Windows 7 systems.

---------------
v0.2
Ability to choose timer (via thumb-bar).
Added plugin support (via MEF, by exporting IPomodoroPublisher).

---------------
v0.1
Initial release.
Switches between 25 and 5 minute timers.
Ability to pause and reset.
